data.description: Well maintained bright airy home. Granite counters and new appliances in the kitchen. Ceramic Tile throughout the living areas with vinyl in the bedrooms no carpet in the house. Newly painted interior. New wall paint in garage wall and new epoxy paint in garage floor .The backyard has an area that the seller put down paving stones to make a nice outdoor seating area or you can enjoy the extended covered porch. Large tree provides shade. The TRE line runs behind the house so there are no neighbors right up against the back of the home. Easy access to 183 and 820 and 114, convenient to Southlake as well
